data.description: Meet Lizzie! She’s a cutie with one of the best covered front porches... it's just perfect for watching the ducks cross the street or the sunset over the darling Clifton Heights Park, only a handful houses away! Nearly 1200 sq ft, 3 bedrooms, formal living & dining rooms, a fully fenced yard with an expansive deck, & a walkout basement. Original hardwood floors, tall baseboards, great front southern exposure, newer windows, & updated systems are some do our favorite features. Main level has a sizable living room with fireplace & an archway opening to the dining room. Kitchen has a full suite of SS appliances & leads to the large deck! Upper level has the primary bedroom with double closets, 2 additional bedrooms, & an updated bathroom with linen closet! Lower level has good ceiling height & walks out to the fully fenced yard. Soha Bar & Grill, Joey Bs, Amigo Joes, & Chris' Pancake House are some of our nearby favorites. Minutes from Clayton, Forest Park, Downtown, BJC, SLU, & Wash U!
